<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer12266031687836833690">Chad Gayle has written for literary journals, trade publications, and newspapers. Previously, Chad worked for Poetry Magazine in Chicago and taught English at several colleges including Texas A&amp;M University. Born in Texas, Chad lives in Brooklyn, New York with his wife and two children; Let It Be is his debut novel. </span>

